sequenceDiagram
    participant E as 执行器 (Server 层)
    participant I as InnoDB
    participant R as redo log
    participant B as binlog

    E->>I: 更新 Buffer Pool 中的数据页 (标记脏页)
    I->>I: 写 undo log (旧值)
    Note over R: Prepare 阶段
    I->>R: 写 redo log, 状态 = prepare, 持久化到磁盘
    Note over B: 写 binlog
    E->>B: 写 binlog cache, 提交时 fsync 到磁盘
    Note over R: Commit 阶段
    E->>I: 提交事务
    I->>R: redo log 状态 = commit

    Note over E,B: 崩溃恢复: redo log 处于 prepare 状态时,<br/>binlog 完整 (有对应 XID) 则提交, 否则回滚
